{
  "stem": "24409.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were taken back to motor-- motorcycle policemen, who told us that the had caught fire and it sunk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, it was a catastrophe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People dead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How many dead?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The transports were finished by this when the [INAUDIBLE] was obvious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But fortunately it was not that bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The ship had caught fire, ran-- ran it into a rock-- I've got photos of it-- and everything, everyone was saved.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The luggage was lost.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And now was the trouble what to do with them?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the-- the governor of Rhodes was a-- a friend of Mussolini's and he was a very good man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I spoke to him, and he called Mussolini for permission to keep all these people there, who were shipwrecked and who had nowhere to go anywhere now, and Mussolini agreed to it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know that Mussolini agreed to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know that they were told they can stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were interned now for a month or two on a-- on a-- stadium in Rhodes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The government and the Jewish community fed them through that time and finally they-- they got more steamer with two little [INAUDIBLE] hanging to it brought them to Israel.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I think this trip took about four or five months before they arrived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was our most difficult trip.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a letter in my hands a couple of days ago, which I think is here, of one of my fraternity brothers, who was on the ship, who sends me this-- years apart now-- I saved his life.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was on this ship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a very difficult trip.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yeah, you know, this fire was not a coincidence, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I believed it was the ship was taken not from the [INAUDIBLE], from another organization.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
